ntum coherence; KR, ketoreductase; KS, ketosynthase; MTSL, (1-oxyl-2,2,5,5-tetramethyl-∆3-pyrroline-3-methyl) methanethiosulfonate; NRPS, non-ribosomal peptide synthetase; PKS, polyketide synthase; PMTS, n-propyl methanethiosufonate; Ppant, 4′-phosphopantetheine; PRE, paramagnetic relaxation enhancement; TE, thioesterase},
